{"tid":607104,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【國際賽】C朗踢草頭跌倒插水 向球證投訴","createTime":"2018-03-27T04:10:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-14T15:07:25.000Z","uid":54373,"like":140,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"e9ac193105eabef109ecc08e9deedb5d5bc900e8","tid":607104,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T04:10:18.000Z","msg":"C朗拿度（Cristiano Ronaldo）領軍的葡萄牙在昨日國際賽慘敗，在瑞士中立場鬥褪色勁旅荷蘭，上半場被對手三度破門，換邊後不但未能破蛋，更有球員被逐，最終以0：3敗陣。C朗雖然沒有入球，但仍是今場的焦點，<span style=\"color: red;\">上半場踢中草頭倒地博12碼，惹來非議</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_lW3fx-DF60\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_lW3fx-DF60&d=1i6%2BM0Kai%2BovlyjlPb85JV0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=d1efd09f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_lW3fx-DF60</a><br />\n<br />\nC朗在上半場最令人留下印象的是插水，在30分鐘，他在禁區倒地，起身後十分不滿，向球證投訴，不獲理會。然而，從慢鏡所見，C朗打算在大位射門，但他踢不中皮球，疑似踢中草頭，失平衡跌倒，沒有荷蘭球員碰到他。"},{"pid":"61ee94db52591366fefea57395f22cf762ece24c","tid":607104,"uid":5178,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T04:11:21.000Z","msg":"型"},{"pid":"61e2129b5c32e043375068653f73d5d56c04e604","tid":607104,"uid":5843,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T04:25:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb869902cedac5bb9e4c06adf00e12cc70f3c9cf","tid":607104,"uid":48334,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T04:34:44.000Z","msg":"踢空氣不失霸氣"},{"pid":"1cd3181be17c89fb033e481bd69db4229e27c52d","tid":607104,"uid":173397,"like":133,"dislike":0,"score":133,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T04:36:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"177058a35551d61d721996d8d3ea0d64f3992eef","tid":607104,"uid":19552,"like":36,"dislike":1,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T04:37:00.000Z","msg":"友賽都插<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ba73e16d3abb11d2ed766a459377dc9f95ca